name: Environmental Values
info:
Temperature, Pressure, and humidity output every 5 seconds, this averages over 180 readings (15 min) then joins the values into a single payload

This payload is then converted into an sql command in the template node 

Averaged envionmental values are then inserted into the sqlite db
